## lane16 variable

Extracts 16-bit lane from given 32bit uint and returns as unsigned half word \[0x0000 .. 0xffff\].

- Lane \#0: bits 16-31 - Lane \#1: bits 0-15

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
lane16: (x: number, lane: Lane16) => number
```
